[thinking] 
[thinking] I’ve got a potential issue with `TestJndiContext.lookup` returning the database name "h2-jdbcutils-jndi." I’m wondering if that hyphen is acceptable for the mem DB name, but it seems likely. I think a slash replace might be the way to go. Also, I’m considering whether the driver class and context load in `JdbcUtils.loadUserClass` could affect userClassFactories. I'll need to keep an eye on these details!
